{"lastModified":1775541838734,"uri":"c::7646090758::vessel::cf7190e0-7e82-11f0-8aef-6f5139717440","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Croatia\n\nEmbark on a stunning cruise along the Adriatic coast aboard the elegant Azimut S7 Fly, the luxurious motor yacht FELICITA. Designed to offer ultimate comfort and style, this exceptional vessel accommodates up to eight guests in four modern, air-conditioned cabins, each equipped with a TV and premium audio system.\n\nAn experienced captain and attentive hostess are on board to ensure your every need is met, delivering a seamless and personalized yachting experience.\nWhat makes Felicita stand out is her perfect balance of elegance and excitement. The flybridge offers panoramic sea views, while the aft deck provides a spacious area for meals or cocktails with direct access to the hydraulic swim platform, ideal for water activities. Seamless access to the water ensures endless fun on the sea. \n","blueprint":{"name":"FELICITA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::cf7190e0-7e82-11f0-8aef-6f5139717440::assets::5a924190-7e85-11f0-82e9-a3df79b1eab4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cf7190e0-7e82-11f0-8aef-6f5139717440::assets::5a985c10-7e85-11f0-82e9-a3df79b1eab4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cf7190e0-7e82-11f0-8aef-6f5139717440::assets::5a9093e0-7e85-11f0-82e9-a3df79b1eab4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cf7190e0-7e82-11f0-8aef-6f5139717440::assets::5a9a09c0-7e85-11f0-82e9-a3df79b1eab4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cf7190e0-7e82-11f0-8aef-6f5139717440::assets::5a9b4240-7e85-11f0-82e9-a3df79b1eab4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cf7190e0-7e82-11f0-8aef-6f5139717440::assets::5a876c20-7e85-11f0-8709-89caa5038b81/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cf7190e0-7e82-11f0-8aef-6f5139717440::assets::5a9d1700-7e85-11f0-82e9-a3df79b1eab4/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::cf7190e0-7e82-11f0-8aef-6f513971744